<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 18:10:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>解释：阻碍加沙-以色列协议的两条“走廊”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-two-corridors-that-are-stymieing-a-gaza-israel-deal/00000191-7500-d2f3-afdf-7dd97ce70000</link><description>哈马斯长期走私武器的费城走廊沿着加沙-埃及边境延伸，而将加沙地带一分为二的内扎里姆走廊则帮助以色列军队在飞地开展行动</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:55:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-two-corridors-that-are-stymieing-a-gaza-israel-deal/00000191-7500-d2f3-afdf-7dd97ce70000</guid></item><item><title>为寻求谈判突破，哈马斯向真主党施压，要求其加大对以色列的攻击力度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-deal-unlikely-hamas-looking-to-hezbollah-to-increase-pressure-on-israel/00000191-7584-d189-adbb-7d8c3cec0000</link><description>以色列、巴勒斯坦、美国和阿拉伯官员都对达成协议的可能性表示悲观，理由是内塔尼亚胡总理不断增加的要求、哈马斯不愿放弃唯一的筹码，以及叶海亚·辛瓦尔希望引发与真主党和伊朗的地区战争</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:50:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-deal-unlikely-hamas-looking-to-hezbollah-to-increase-pressure-on-israel/00000191-7584-d189-adbb-7d8c3cec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陷入战争第 320 天：据报道，官员称加沙休战谈判“濒临崩溃”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-320-gaza-truce-talks-on-brink-of-collapse-officials-reportedly-say/00000191-75b5-d8d0-a7bb-fdb573d00000</link><description>参与谈判的消息人士告诉《国土报》，内塔尼亚胡“再次破坏与哈马斯的人质释放/停火协议谈判” ■ 真主党向以色列北部发射了约 50 枚火箭，造成一名男子中度受伤 ■ 六个加沙边境社区、人质家庭论坛宣布他们将抵制政府组织的 10 月 7 日大屠杀纪念仪式 ■ 这是战争 320 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-320-gaza-truce-talks-on-brink-of-collapse-officials-reportedly-say/00000191-75b5-d8d0-a7bb-fdb573d00000</guid></item><item><title>巨型鸟类如何在空气稀薄的高空停留</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/how-giant-birds-stay-aloft-at-great-heights-where-the-air-is-thin/00000191-7595-daab-a3f3-f59784c50000</link><description>在七英里高的地方，您从喷气式客机的窗户向外望去，与秃鹰四目相对。这种情况非常罕见，但确实发生了。那些秃头美女是怎么呆在上面的？</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 16:44:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/how-giant-birds-stay-aloft-at-great-heights-where-the-air-is-thin/00000191-7595-daab-a3f3-f59784c50000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列执意要拆散这些乌克兰家庭？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-is-israel-insisting-on-breaking-these-ukrainian-families-up/00000191-7401-dabe-a597-ff2bd1170000</link><description>尽管安娜在乌克兰战争中丧生的丈夫是以色列公民，但她无法在以色列获得合法地位。扎哈尔计划加入以色列国防军，像哥哥一样去加沙服役，但入籍申请未获批准</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 15:34:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-is-israel-insisting-on-breaking-these-ukrainian-families-up/00000191-7401-dabe-a597-ff2bd1170000</guid></item><item><title>以色列前特使称联合国“没有必要，应该从地球上抹去”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/former-israeli-envoy-to-un-calls-it-unnecessary-and-should-be-wiped-off-the-earth/00000191-7557-dc26-a9d7-f5dfb56f0000</link><description>即将离任的以色列驻联合国大使吉拉德·埃尔丹表示，“没有哪个地方比联合国更腐败和道德扭曲了。”他在任期内习惯于发表有争议的花招和言论。他敦促各国团结起来，要求“关闭和解散”联合国</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 15:26:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/former-israeli-envoy-to-un-calls-it-unnecessary-and-should-be-wiped-off-the-earth/00000191-7557-dc26-a9d7-f5dfb56f0000</guid></item><item><title>因哄抬物价受到批评后，以色列航空公司将出售飞往四个目的地的固定价格机票</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/following-criticism-el-al-to-sell-fixed-price-tickets-to-four-destinations/00000191-750f-daab-a3f3-f58f07f30000</link><description>该航空公司将运营飞往拉纳卡、迪拜、雅典和维也纳的固定价格航班，以色列人可以在那里转乘飞往其他国家的航班。该决定是在以色列航空公司首席执行官与经济部长尼尔·巴尔卡特交谈后宣布的</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 14:02:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/following-criticism-el-al-to-sell-fixed-price-tickets-to-four-destinations/00000191-750f-daab-a3f3-f58f07f30000</guid></item><item><title>人质母亲：哈马斯应该劫持以色列高层的儿子来换取人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/hostages-mother-hamas-should-take-sons-of-israels-top-brass-in-exchange-for-hostages/00000191-74a0-d8ab-a1f5-7efc4e2e0000</link><description>主持人为没有缩短电视直播讲话而道歉，母亲迪扎·奥尔 (Ditza Or) 在讲话中提出将她认为代表 10 月 7 日失败的人的儿子交给哈马斯</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 12:18:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/hostages-mother-hamas-should-take-sons-of-israels-top-brass-in-exchange-for-hostages/00000191-74a0-d8ab-a1f5-7efc4e2e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的战争目标不是人质返回。这是对加沙的占领</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-war-goal-is-not-the-hostages-return-its-the-occupation-of-gaza/00000191-7477-d7fc-ab93-f67774cb0000</link><description>以色列对约旦河西岸 57 年的占领告诉我们，明天不会在加沙建立大型犹太城市； “蠕动占领”将推动一个又一个商队、一个又一个前哨基地</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 11:37:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-war-goal-is-not-the-hostages-return-its-the-occupation-of-gaza/00000191-7477-d7fc-ab93-f67774cb0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗窃取以色列敏感数据后，以色列试图审查互联网</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-futile-war-against-massive-iranian-hack-of-secret-data/00000191-6bd7-d1ee-afb5-6bff8a510000</link><description>反以色列黑客窃取了大量以色列敏感数据，现在正在发布数十亿字节的秘密和机密信息。由于无法阻止黑客攻击，以色列正在发动一场徒劳的战争来阻止泄密</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:35:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-futile-war-against-massive-iranian-hack-of-secret-data/00000191-6bd7-d1ee-afb5-6bff8a510000</guid></item><item><title>来自黎巴嫩的火箭弹袭击导致以色列北部一名以色列人受伤；以色列国防军袭击真主党目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/rocket-barrage-leaves-one-wounded-in-israels-north-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets/00000191-741c-dadb-a1f9-7cff20c70000</link><description>50 枚火箭弹猛烈攻击以色列北部，造成大面积破坏并引发火灾，导致一名男子遭受弹片和电击伤。以色列国防军发言人丹尼尔·哈加里表示，“真主党再次向以色列平民肆意开火”，并补充说以色列“将采取相应行动”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:14:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/rocket-barrage-leaves-one-wounded-in-israels-north-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets/00000191-741c-dadb-a1f9-7cff20c70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列科学家发明了独特高效的系统来同时种植鱼类和蔬菜</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/israeli-scientists-invent-revolutionary-system-to-grow-fish-and-vegetables-together/00000191-7414-dadb-a1f9-7cff28fb0000</link><description>气候变化正在给我们的食物来源带来压力。本古里安大学的科学家开发了先进的鱼菜共生系统，我们吃的蔬菜生长在我们也吃的鱼的排泄物中 - 并且它产生能量</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 09:50:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/israeli-scientists-invent-revolutionary-system-to-grow-fish-and-vegetables-together/00000191-7414-dadb-a1f9-7cff28fb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属和加沙附近的基布兹抵制国营 10 月 7 日守夜活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/three-additional-gaza-border-communities-bow-out-of-state-run-oct-7-vigil/00000191-73cc-d180-a5f5-73cf20e70000</link><description>加沙边境附近的六个基布兹宣布将抵制由交通部长米里·雷格夫（Miri Regev）领导的仪式</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 09:44:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/three-additional-gaza-border-communities-bow-out-of-state-run-oct-7-vigil/00000191-73cc-d180-a5f5-73cf20e70000</guid></item><item><title>极端正统派抗议者在耶路撒冷以色列军队征兵办公室外与警察发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-protesters-clash-with-police-outside-israeli-armys-base-in-jerusalem/00000191-73fa-db7d-a7d7-7ffabf380000</link><description>警方向示威者喷洒所谓的臭鼬水，并逮捕了几名抗议者。以色列军队最近开始向犹太学院学生发送征兵通知，以回应最高法院的裁决</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 08:53:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-protesters-clash-with-police-outside-israeli-armys-base-in-jerusalem/00000191-73fa-db7d-a7d7-7ffabf380000</guid></item><item><title>在内塔尼亚胡看来，以色列人质绝不是一种资产</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/as-far-as-netanyahu-is-concerned-the-hostages-are-anything-but-an-asset/00000191-71c7-dabe-a597-fbef42bb0000</link><description>总理正在就释放人质进行谈判，却没有考虑谁应该对他们的被囚禁负责，就好像他们走错了方向，最终进入了加沙的隧道一样。虽然辩方正在谈论价值观，但对他来说只有一个价值观很重要：生存</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 03:00:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/as-far-as-netanyahu-is-concerned-the-hostages-are-anything-but-an-asset/00000191-71c7-dabe-a597-fbef42bb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列即将离任的军事情报局局长呼吁成立委员会对 10 月 7 日事件进行调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-live/report-idf-attacks-deep-inside-lebanon-after-dozens-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel/00000191-72b6-d5c0-afb3-f3f7bdf00000</link><description>拜登与内塔尼亚胡周三通话讨论加沙停火 ■ 加沙卫生部：自战争爆发以来，加沙已有 40,223 人死亡、92,981 人受伤 ■ 内塔尼亚胡誓言以色列空军已做好应对以色列北部任何情况的准备 ■ 以色列国防军称其击毙了伊斯兰革命卫队黎巴嫩武装分子，战斗机在一夜之间杀死了真主党武装分子 ■ 内塔尼亚胡对协议表示怀疑，坚称以色列控制加沙-埃及边境；哈马斯批评美国提议</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 02:24:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-live/report-idf-attacks-deep-inside-lebanon-after-dozens-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel/00000191-72b6-d5c0-afb3-f3f7bdf00000</guid></item><item><title>民主党人相信，无论特朗普和共和党怎么说，犹太人的选票坚定地对他们有利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/democrats-believe-the-jewish-vote-is-solidly-in-their-favor-no-matter-what-trump-says/00000191-725a-d8ab-a1f5-7a7e456a0000</link><description>一位研究犹太投票模式的专家表示，“犹太选民毫不犹豫地表示，批评以色列政府政策并仍然支持以色列是可以的”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 00:51:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/democrats-believe-the-jewish-vote-is-solidly-in-their-favor-no-matter-what-trump-says/00000191-725a-d8ab-a1f5-7a7e456a0000</guid></item><item><title>参与停火谈判的消息人士称内塔尼亚胡“再次破坏谈判”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/sources-involved-in-cease-fire-negotiations-say-netanyahu-is-once-again-sabotaging-talks/00000191-7168-dadb-a1f9-7dfb63870000</link><description>一位消息人士称，总理在会见死者家属时的言论“使达成协议变得更加困难，增加了怀疑，并向哈马斯和调解人发出信号，表明内塔尼亚胡对达成协议不感兴趣。”本周在埃及举行的峰会日期尚未确定</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 20:55:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/sources-involved-in-cease-fire-negotiations-say-netanyahu-is-once-again-sabotaging-talks/00000191-7168-dadb-a1f9-7dfb63870000</guid></item><item><title>以色列央行行长敦促内塔尼亚胡因延迟问题启动2025年预算</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/bank-of-israel-governor-urges-netanyahu-to-start-the-2025-budget-amid-delay-concerns/00000191-7126-dadb-a1f9-7dff19fa0000</link><description>鉴于最近举行的预算会议没有专业公务员的充分参与，以色列央行行长阿米尔·亚龙教授致信内塔尼亚胡，对推迟批准明年的预算表示担忧</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 20:36:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/bank-of-israel-governor-urges-netanyahu-to-start-the-2025-budget-amid-delay-concerns/00000191-7126-dadb-a1f9-7dff19fa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击学校和市场，造成至少 20 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，其中包括儿童</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/at-least-20-palestinians-including-children-killed-in-israeli-strikes-on-school-market/00000191-70fd-d8ab-a1f5-7afd080d0000</link><description>代尔巴拉赫市场罢工现场的目击者称，大多数伤亡者是儿童。以色列国防军在评论造成 12 人死亡的学校袭击事件时表示，袭击目标是哈马斯指挥中心</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 20:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/at-least-20-palestinians-including-children-killed-in-israeli-strikes-on-school-market/00000191-70fd-d8ab-a1f5-7afd080d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>